There are only 6 items that give movespeed other than boots. 3 of which are attack speed items, 2 are AP and the last is triforce.
{{item:3087}} {{item:3046}} {{item:3078}} {{item:3172}} {{item:3100}} {{item:3023}} 

Its dangerous to give tanks permanent movespeed bonuses because they have to be "kiteable". There are no "tank" items that grant permanent movespeed in the game.
